            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> Caesari divi Septimi Sev<supplied reason="lost">eri Pii Felicis <expan><abbr>Arab</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Adiab</abbr><ex>enici</ex></expan> Parthici</supplied> <lb n="2"/>maximi Britannici maximi <supplied reason="lost">filio</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><del rend="erasure">[<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/></del>] <supplied reason="lost">divi <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> Aureli</supplied> Anto<lb break="no" n="4"/>nini Pii Germanici Sarmatici nepoti <supplied reason="lost">divi Antonini Pii pron</supplied>epoti <lb n="5"/>divi Hadriani abnepoti divi Trai<supplied reason="lost">ani Parthici et divi N</supplied>ervae <lb n="6"/>adnepoti a <del rend="erasure"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Septimio Getae</del> et <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">I</supplied>u<supplied reason="lost">lia</supplied>e <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> Piae Felici matri <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> et <supplied reason="lost">castrorum et senatus</supplied> et patriae </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ------ milites] <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">vexillationis</supplied> <lb n="3"/>An<supplied reason="lost">toninianorum</supplied> <lb n="4"/>Europa<supplied reason="lost">eorum</supplied> <lb n="5"/>devoti num<supplied reason="lost">ini</supplied> <lb n="6"/>maiestatique <lb n="7"/>eius
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Y: Febr. 211: Tod des Severus; Dez. 211: Ermordung Getas. (B): [senatus] / [Aureliorum]; (C): Es handelt sich um zwei Inschriften, die nebeneinander gesetzt wurden. 2. Inschrift als Ergänzung der 1. (A): AE 1984: Falsche bibliographische Angaben. (B): AE 1934 gibt nur zweiten Teil der Inschrift wieder (= AE 1984, 921 b). (C): Datierung: 211-212. In den Buchstaben Spuren roter Farbe. 6 aneinanderpassende Fragmente. Z.7 Anfang: bei Iuliae Widerspruch zwischen Umzeichnung und Wiedergabe des Textes.</p>
            </div>
